criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Patients with unstable vital sign or by other physiological or mental reasons can not undergo MRI exam;
2. Relatives of the patient refuse to join this research;
3. Patients with other diseases which can lead to iron overload;
4. Patients with other diseases in liver or heart(ie. neoplasms);
5. patients have inflamation, liver disease, heart failure or arrhythmia.
